<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/20178265-pillar-of-light"><img alt="Pillar of Light (The Work and the Glory #1)" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1462605727l/20178265._SX98_.jpg" />
